 *         - the data for each id, padded to 32B each
 *
 *            +-----------------------+ offset: 0
 *            | 32B reserved          |
 *            +-----------------------+ offset: 1 = end of first 32B
 *            |      (ID1,offset1)    |
 *            |      (ID2,offset2)    |
 *            |       0's padding     |
 *            +-----------------------+ offset: offset1 = 1 + number of words taken by the padded table
 *            |       id1 data1       |
 *            | 0's padding           |
 *            +-----------------------+ offset: offset2 = offset1 + number of words taken by the data1
 *            |       id2 data2       |
 *            | 0's padding           |
 *            +-----------------------+
